data.description: Welcome Home! Newly updated 3-bedroom brick ranch. Excellent Southgate Location. Close to several restaurants and shopping areas. Southgate school district. Kitchen features real marble floor. New a/c and furnace. New roof in 2019 and almost all of the windows were replaced in 2021. Two car detached garage for additional storage. Buyer to assume city repairs.
